channel.title: Why Ain't It Working!?! (Help Is Rewarded!)
channel.description:
You help me out, you get auto-admin. Here's the problem, I want a no-ip, non-hamachi server. I've read ALL the tuts on making a priv. server. So I got the No-IP client on my windows, I portforwarded, and then I ran the server. WTF isn't it working? Alright, so I prefer LIVE messeging so I can do this faster, I need one of ya'll to give me step-by-step directions on how to portforward, no-ip, and run the server. My MSN messenger is thekeepa@hotmail.com
Thanks, Play For Keeps
